(x^2 + x + 1)
f(x) = (x+1)^{2n+1} + x^{n+2}
f(\omega) = (\omega+1)^{2n+1} + \omega^{n+2} = (-\omega^2)^{2n+1} + \omega^{n+2} = \omega^{4n} (-\omega^2) + \omega^{n+2} = \omega^{n+2} \left( 1 - \omega^{3n}\right) = 0
f(\omega^2) = (\omega^2+1)^{2n+1} + \omega^{2(n+2)} = (-\omega)^{2n+1} + \omega^{2n+4} = -\omega^{2n+1} + \omega^{2n+1} \omega^3 = -\omega^{2n+1} + \omega^{2n+1} = 0
